33:19.720 --> 33:20.400
Platform e-panggilan

33:20.400 --> 33:23.510
tiada rekod e-panggilan
daripada nombor telefon Luo Liang.

33:23.510 --> 33:24.680
Kakak, tunggu sekejap.

33:24.680 --> 33:25.480
Mentor.

33:25.480 --> 33:26.830
Tunggu sekejap.

33:27.070 --> 33:27.960
Mentor!

33:28.920 --> 33:29.920
Kakak, cakaplah.

33:30.070 --> 33:31.920
Melalui CCTV di rumah,

33:32.190 --> 33:33.590
